          <li><%= setting(:abbreviation) %> papers are required to have a <a href="https://joss.readthedocs.io/en/latest/submitting.html#what-should-my-paper-contain">list of references</a>, and <a href="https://joss.readthedocs.io/en/latest/submitting.html#what-should-my-paper-contain">financial support</a>.</li>

